{"id":101,"name":"Al-Qari'ah","nameArabic":"القارعة","transliteration":"Al-Qari'ah","type":"meccan","ayahCount":11,"verses":[{"n":1,"text":"ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","translit":"AlqariAAatu","translation":"The Striking Calamity"},{"n":2,"text":"مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","translit":"Ma alqariAAatu","translation":"What is the Striking Calamity"},{"n":3,"text":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","translit":"Wama adraka ma alqariAAatu","translation":"And what can make you know what is the Striking Calamity"},{"n":4,"text":"يَوۡمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلۡفَرَاشِ ٱلۡمَبۡثُوثِ","translit":"Yawma yakoonu alnnasu kaalfarashi almabthoothi","translation":"It is the Day when people will be like moths, dispersed"},{"n":5,"text":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ ٱلۡمَنفُوشِ","translit":"Watakoonu aljibalu kaalAAihni almanfooshi","translation":"And the mountains will be like wool, fluffed up"},{"n":6,"text":"فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","translit":"Faamma man thaqulat mawazeenuhu","translation":"Then as for one whose scales are heavy [with good deeds]"},{"n":7,"text":"فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ","translit":"Fahuwa fee AAeeshatin radiyatin","translation":"He will be in a pleasant life"},{"n":8,"text":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","translit":"Waamma man khaffat mawazeenuhu","translation":"But as for one whose scales are light"},{"n":9,"text":"فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٞ","translit":"Faommuhu hawiyatun","translation":"His refuge will be an abyss"},{"n":10,"text":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهۡ","translit":"Wama adraka ma hiyah","translation":"And what can make you know what that is"},{"n":11,"text":"نَارٌ حَامِيَةُۢ","translit":"Narun hamiyatun","translation":"It is a Fire, intensely hot"}]}